  "texts": [
    "This involves parallel processing across multiple GPUs, which enhances the efficiency and scalability of the training process.",
    "Effective synchronization mechanisms are employed to ensure consistency and stability during the learning phase.",
    "4) Continuous Evaluation and Adjustment: Throughout the training process, continuous evaluation metrics are applied to monitor the performance of the model across all modalities.",
    "Adjustments are made dynamically to the training regimen based on these evaluations to optimize model performance and ensure that integration of modalities improves over time.",
    "5) Fine-Tuning and Validation: After the initial multimodal training phases, the model undergoes fine-tuning with more specific tasks and datasets."
